@startuml phase1_init
title Phase 1 — Initialization & Vector Clock Broadcast

participant Browser
participant Orchestrator
participant "Fraud Detection" as FD
participant "Transaction Verification" as TV
participant Suggestions as SG

== Initialization (parallel) ==

Browser -> Orchestrator : POST /checkout

Orchestrator -> FD : init
Orchestrator <-- FD : completion_vc

Orchestrator -> TV : init
Orchestrator <-- TV : completion_vc

Orchestrator -> SG : init
Orchestrator <-- SG : completion_vc

== Vector Clock Broadcast ==

Orchestrator -> FD : broadcast_vc
Orchestrator -> TV : broadcast_vc
Orchestrator -> SG : broadcast_vc
@enduml
